--- BLCeStats - Trader1 ---
Multi Threaded Bitcoin and Litecoin Ticker Application
Feeds from MTGox, BTC-e, BTCChina, OKCoin
Buy Price, Volume, Spread, Change
Uses .Net Charting to show BTC/LTC Price as line chart
Conversion to USD Currency from Yuan - Feed From OpenExchangeRates.org
Clocks from New York, London, Beijing
Run and watch data build up - use to help decision making when trading
ASK / BIDS : $TotalAmount #AverageCoins -from BTCe with Percentage